    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small arms projectiles, including bullets and cartridges, containing a substance that ignites at the point of impact, designed to penetrate and set fire especially to aircraft, vehicles, buildings, and installations.</Note_Text>
